<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.9">
<l>vārāḷu miḷaṅkoṅkai neṭumpaṇaittōḷ maṭappāvai</l>
<l>cīrāḷum varaimārvaṉ tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>pērāḷa ṉāyirampē rāyiravā yaravaṇaimēl</l>
<l>pērāḷar perumāṉuk kiḻantēṉeṉ peyvaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my bangles that [I] wore to the great lord of great men</l>
<l>On a thousand-headed serpent bed, the great man of a thousand names,</l>
<l>Who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram, the one on whose mountain chest,</l>
<l rend="indent">possessed of renown,</l>
<l>Is the simple girl with long bamboo arms</l>
<l rend="indent">and bandeau-governed young breasts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
